@node "ACTION FIGHTER"
ACTION FIGHTER

Get on the hi-score table and enter ZBACKDOOR for infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "AFTERBURNER"
AFTERBURNER

Pause the game , then type THUNDERBLADE. Then try the following keys:

  < - Go down a level
  > - Go up a level
  G - More Missiles
  T - Less Missiles
  N - Extra Lives

Fly to the top of the screeen to avoid missiles.  Slow down on levels
8 and 17 to avoid rocks.  Go full speed to dodge infra-red missiles.

Note: Other sources say type TOGETHER IN ELECTRIC DREAMS
@endnode
@node "AFTER THE WAR"
AFTER THE WAR

To give yourself infinite energy & time, press the following three keys 
simultaneously on level 1;

  Hold down the  ALT, 1, B  keys.

  Holding down the  ALT, 1, M  keys advances you to the second level.

  The password for Level 2 is 101069.
@endnode
@node "AIRBALL"
AIRBALL

The spellbook is in the room with the candle. You have to pick up 
and remove the blocks to get it. Take the spellbook back to the 
start screen and drop it in the top left corner and follow the 
instructions to get the ingredients to complete the game. 
@endnode
@node "A.P.B."
A.P.B.

Type ALF into the hi-score table for infinite demerits.

If you hold down the button while driving, the siren will sound,
and the other cars will move out of the way. Now you can drive at
full speed without crashing.
@endnode
@node "ARCHIPELAGOS"
ARCHIPELAGOS

When asked to select an Archipelagos choose 8421 then press the ENTER key
twice. Now you can select any island from 1 to 9999.

Another source says you must play the first two levels before activating
the above sequence.
@endnode
@node "ARKANOID"
ARKANOID

Start the game as usual, and while playing the game, you can access
the cheat mode by doing the following.

Pause the game with the Space Bar. Now type 'DSIMAGIC' (do not hit return)
and press Space to unpause the game.

A yellow capsule, 'DS' will fall. Catch it. Now the following keys
will make the following capsules fall at any time.

[B] - Break        (Opens gates and awards bonus points)
[C] - Catch        (Holds ball)
[D] - Disruption   (Split into 3 balls)
[E] - Expand       (Makes vaus larger)
[L] - Laser        (Gives you a laser used with mouse button)
[P] - Extra Player (Self Explanatory)
[S] - Slow         (Slows down ball)

In addition, pressing 'F' will send you to the last level to fight DOH.
Be sure to give yourself lots of lives first.

You can skip any level by using ENTER on the keypad.

To access the extra 33 levels (assuming you have that version), press F3
for a one player game and F4 for a two player game. (instead of F1 or F2)
@endnode
@node "ARKANOID II"
ARKANOID II

On the high score screen, type 'DEBBIE S' for unlimited lives.

When you die, wait until the title screen appears. Press CAPS LOCK, then
type 'DALEY-88'.  You will then continue on the same level you died on.

On the title page, type 'ROBOCOPPETER' for continuous mode.

When you die, wait until the title screen appears. Press CAPS LOCK, then
type 'MAGENTA'.  Now when playing, hit 'S' to skip levels.
@endnode
@node "ARKANOID 3, Revenge Of Doh (Imagine)"
ARKANOID 3, Revenge Of Doh (Imagine)
 
When the pink loading screen appears, hold down Caps Lock and type IMAGINE.
When the opening bit plays, type PETEJOHNSONWANTSCHEAT.  Now, when you press
S, it causes both exits to open, and you can go on to the next screen without
finishing it.  Or, type DALEY88 instead at the pink screen, and you can now
restart at the level you last died on!
@endnode
@node "ASTRO MARINE CORP"
ASTRO MARINE CORP

Passwords:   Zone 2:   NOSTROMO
             Zone 4:   DISCOVERY
             Zone 6:   ENTERPRISE
             Zone 8:   DAGOBAH
             Zone 10:   REPLICANT
             Zone 12:  KRULL
             Zone 14:  METROPOLIS
@endnode
@node "ATOMIC ROBO KID (Activision)"
ATOMIC ROBO KID (Activision)

While still on the title screen type in TUESDAY 14TH (with the space) and
when you press fire to start the game you will be presented with an options
sreen that will allow you to obtain infinite lives, etc.
@endnode
@node "AWESOME"
AWESOME

Hold down the  + key on the keypad and press Fire. Then during play F1 key
disables enemies, F6 replenishes energy and 1-10 keys give you different 
weapons.
@endnode
@node "BAAL"
BAAL

During the load push the right mouse button for infinite lives as the screen
blanks.

In the second cavern there is a force filed that seems impossible to get
rid of. To get to the time machine chunk beyond it, simply fall off the
right side of the phone booth platform above.

Here are all the coordinates of all the jetpack platforms, in the order you
should go to them to finish the game.  X/Y, X being width and Y being height:

    Level 1:  31/16 (cartridge 2), 02/25, 52/30 (cartridge 3), 51/00, 24/38,
62/13, 02/50, 64/49, 33/58 (exit to level 2).

    Level 2:  34/30, 54/12 (cartridge 4), 16/12, 00/24, 03/34, 30/47, 54/12
(exit to level 3).

    The jetpack isn't used on level 3.

@endnode
@node "BACK TO THE FUTURE II"
BACK TO THE FUTURE II

Pause the action at any time and type  THE ONLY NEAT THING TO DO (include
spaces). The game will reset, indicating the cheat mode is active.
Now you have infinite lives.
@endnode
@node "BARBARIAN (Psygnosis)"
BARBARIAN (Psygnosis)

During the game, type '04-08-59'.  The screen should turn grey.
If so, you are now invulnerable and have unlimited lives.

NOTE: Other sources say code is `04 08 59' no hyphens between numbers:

To kill the final Wizard, you must have a shield. When his shot comes
at you, use the defense icon, and it will fly back at him.
@endnode
@node "BARBARIAN II (Palace)  step-by-step walk-thru"
BARBARIAN II (Palace)  step-by-step walk-thru
 
Level 1:  left, left, right seven times, left, right, left, in the cave,
and right.  Level 2:  right, up, left, up, left, left, right, left three
times, up, and left.  Level 3:  up, right, right, up, left, right, up, right,
left, left, up, left, left, up, up, right, right, left, left, up.  Level 4:
hit the fireballs, then try to leap across.  Several low chops will destroy
it.  Next is the Pit Demon; when he reaches out, use an overhead chop to hit
his arms; repeat until death.  Next, Drax himself!  Wait until he pauses
between spells, and hit him with a flying head chop!  The End...
@endnode
@node "BARD'S TALE"
BARD'S TALE

Load your party, go to the statistics screen for the first player.
Pool all of the party's gold to the first player, then remove him from
the party, and then load him back in.  Then pool the gold to another
player. Repeat this for each player.

Turn off the computer without saving the game and every player will
have the gold of the entire party before. Repeat if wanted.
@endnode
@node "BATMAM THE MOVIE"
BATMAM THE MOVIE

While the title page is displayed (one with Batman & Joker, type 'JAMMMM'.
Hold down each key several seconds and last M key should turn screen
upside down.  The words 'CHEAT MODE ON' should appear at the top of the 
screen.  You also have unlimited lives.  Press F10 to skip levels.
@endnode
@node "BATTLE SQUADRON"
BATTLE SQUADRON

Type ELECTRONIC on the intro to call up the game options editor.

Type in CASTOR during play- the screen will flash green indicating
the cheat mode is active. Both ships are now invincible.
Pressing F6 - F10 will select different types of weapons.
         F1 - F5 will alter its power.
@endnode
@node "BATTLE VALLEY"
BATTLE VALLEY

Type ROGER MELLIE THE MAN ON THE TELE activates infinite lives cheat.
@endnode
@node "BEACH VOLLEY"
BEACH VOLLEY

Type 'DADDYBRACEY' to activate the level skip option.
The screen should flash. Press F1 to skip levels.
NOTE: May have a space like DADDY BRACEY
@endnode
@node "BETTER DEAD THAN ALIEN"
BETTER DEAD THAN ALIEN

Typing CHAMP then pressing HELP will show you the cheats available.

  Keys for cheating:   F1 - Scatterbolts     F6 - Neutron Bomb
                       F2 - Multi Fire       F7 - Clone Ship
                       F3 - Auto Repeat      F8 - Shield
                       F4 - Armour Missles   F9 - Skip Level
                       F5 - Stun             F0 - Extra Power Bars

If the passwords are extened  into the names of the programmers,
ELVIE and CHAMPIE, the program states that the 'Supercheat' has
been entered.  If anyone finds out just exactly this does, drop
me a line, eh?

Here's the complete set of codes for both the ST and Amiga 
versions.

LEVEL       PASSWORD           COMMENT
-----       --------           -------
001         ELEKTRA            PRACTICE
002         SYZYGY             A DODDLE
003         DRAMBUIE           VERY EASY
004         PLUG               EASY
