Click past the high score screen onto the select difficulty page.
Type MELLIE and you will be able to access all the games.
@endnode
@node "BIO CHALLENGE"
BIO CHALLENGE

Pause with ESC and G key will advance you to the end of level guardian
(as if you want to go there).
@endnode
@node "BOMBUZAL"
BOMBUZAL

