INDIANA JONES & THE LAST CRUSADE (US Gold) - Arcade version

If Indy has trouble beating the evil Nazis, simply type:  JEHOVA when
the title screen appears.  The screen will flash momentarily, indicating
that the cheat is activated. Now simply press  'L'  when you want to skip
