Hold down Enter on the keypad, and press P to pause.  Continue holding Enter
down and press O to unpause.  Everything will look normal except for an extra
bar below the altitude gauge.  Pressing the following keys:

    C - special F/Xs on/off, 
    D - demo on/off, 
    F - refuels you completely, 
    L - adds one missile every time it's pressed, 
    N - turns cheat off. 
